    <para id="id9220923">We are all aware that smoking is bad for ones health. Even passive smokers are greatly harmed by people who smoke in their presence. Use an old medicine bottle to manufacture an anti-smoking sign. The drawing must contain a circuit that will draw the attention of smokers. You can make use of a flickering LED to make the sign more effective.</para>
    <para id="id4034193">Assessment</para>
